[SN]TITLE[SN]
What is the future direction of Europe?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Following the shock of Brexit and the election of the openly hostile Donald Trump, will the EU come closer together or is the path forward one of looser cooperation?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
17 March 2017 Last updated at 15:22 GMT
MEPs in Strasbourg have been looking at five options laid out by the European Commission in a White Paper.
Dan Johnson takes a look for Politics Europe.
